<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Proof — A Data Study of What the World Drinks</title>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/d3/7.8.5/d3.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/topojson/3.0.2/topojson.min.js"></script>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400;1,600&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@300;400;500&family=Instrument+Sans:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
:root{
  --bg:#0e0c0a;
  --bg2:#141210;
  --bg3:#1a1714;
  --surface:#201d19;
  --border:rgba(255,240,200,0.08);
  --border2:rgba(255,240,200,0.14);
  --text:#f0ead8;
  --muted:#8a7f6a;
  --dim:#4a4238;
  --beer:#d4931e;
  --beer-dim:rgba(212,147,30,0.15);
  --spirits:#c0392b;
  --spirits-dim:rgba(192,57,43,0.15);
  --wine:#8e44ad;
  --wine-dim:rgba(142,68,173,0.15);
  --gold:#d4b896;
  --accent:#e8c97a;
}

html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:'Instrument Sans',sans-serif;overflow-x:hidden;line-height:1.6}

/* ─ SCROLL PROGRESS ─ */
#progress{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;height:2px;background:var(--accent);z-index:9999;transition:width 0.1s linear;width:0}

/* ─ NAV ─ */
nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:100;padding:0 48px;height:56px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;background:rgba(14,12,10,0.85);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.nav-brand{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:300;letter-spacing:0.05em;color:var(--accent)}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:32px}
.nav-links a{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;transition:color 0.2s}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--text)}

/* ─ HERO ─ */
.hero{min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:flex-end;padding:0 80px 80px;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.hero-bg{position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 60% 40%,rgba(212,147,30,0.06) 0%,transparent 60%),radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 40% at 20% 80%,rgba(192,57,43,0.05) 0%,transparent 50%)}
.hero-counter{position:absolute;top:50%;right:80px;transform:translateY(-50%);text-align:right}
.hero-num{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(120px,18vw,220px);font-weight:300;line-height:1;color:transparent;-webkit-text-stroke:1px rgba(212,184,150,0.15);letter-spacing:-0.04em;user-select:none}
.hero-eyebrow{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.25em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:20px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
.hero-eyebrow::before{content:'';display:block;width:40px;height:1px;background:var(--accent)}
h1.hero-title{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(56px,9vw,130px);font-weight:300;line-height:0.9;letter-spacing:-0.03em;max-width:900px}
h1.hero-title em{font-style:italic;color:var(--accent)}
.hero-sub{margin-top:32px;max-width:520px;font-size:15px;font-weight:400;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.75}
.hero-meta{display:flex;gap:40px;margin-top:40px;padding-top:32px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.hero-meta-item{}
.hero-meta-label{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--dim);margin-bottom:4px}
.hero-meta-val{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:300;color:var(--gold)}
.hero-meta-unit{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-left:4px}
.scroll-hint{position:absolute;bottom:40px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.2em;color:var(--dim);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:8px;animation:bobble 2s ease-in-out infinite}
.scroll-hint::after{content:'';display:block;width:1px;height:40px;background:linear-gradient(var(--dim),transparent)}
@keyframes bobble{0%,100%{transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(0)}50%{transform:translateX(-50%) translateY(6px)}}

/* ─ SECTION SKELETON ─ */
.section{padding:120px 80px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);position:relative}
.section-label{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.3em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:16px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
.section-label::before{content:attr(data-n);font-size:10px;color:var(--dim)}
h2.section-title{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,72px);font-weight:300;line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:24px}
h2.section-title em{font-style:italic;color:var(--accent)}
.section-body{font-size:15px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8;max-width:640px;margin-bottom:56px}
.section-body strong{color:var(--text);font-weight:500}
.callout{border-left:2px solid var(--accent);padding:16px 24px;margin:32px 0;background:rgba(212,184,150,0.04)}
.callout-text{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:22px;font-style:italic;line-height:1.5;color:var(--gold)}
.callout-source{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--dim);margin-top:8px}

/* ─ TWO-COL ─ */
.two-col{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:64px;align-items:start}
.three-col{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:32px}

/* ─ STAT BLOCK ─ */
.stat-block{padding:32px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--surface);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.stat-block::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:var(--sb-color,var(--accent))}
.stat-num{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:56px;font-weight:300;line-height:1;color:var(--sb-color,var(--accent))}
.stat-label{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-top:8px}
.stat-note{font-size:12px;color:var(--dim);margin-top:8px;line-height:1.5}

/* ─ CHART CONTAINERS ─ */
.chart-wrap{width:100%;position:relative}
.chart-title{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:16px;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;justify-content:space-between}
.chart-note{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--dim);margin-top:10px}

/* ─ BAR CHART (custom) ─ */
.bar-chart{}
.bar-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:140px 1fr 52px;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:8px;cursor:default}
.bar-row:hover .bar-fill{filter:brightness(1.2)}
.bar-name{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);text-overflow:ellipsis;overflow:hidden;white-space:nowrap;text-align:right}
.bar-track{height:8px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;position:relative}
.bar-fill{height:100%;border-radius:4px;transition:width 1s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1);width:0}
.bar-val{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);text-align:right}

/* ─ STACKED BAR ─ */
.stacked-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:130px 1fr 60px;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:10px}
.stacked-name{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);text-align:right;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis;white-space:nowrap}
.stacked-track{height:12px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden;display:flex}
.stacked-seg{height:100%;transition:width 1s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1);width:0}
.stacked-total{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted);text-align:right}

/* ─ MATRIX / HEATMAP ─ */
.matrix-wrap{overflow-x:auto}
.matrix-table{border-collapse:collapse;font-size:11px;width:100%}
.matrix-table th{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--dim);padding:6px 10px;text-align:center;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.matrix-table th:first-child{text-align:left}
.matrix-table td{padding:8px 10px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);font-size:12px}
.matrix-table td:first-child{color:var(--muted);font-size:12px}
.matrix-table td:not(:first-child){text-align:center;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;transition:background 0.3s}
.heat-0{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.01);color:var(--dim)}
.heat-1{background:rgba(212,147,30,0.12);color:rgba(212,147,30,0.6)}
.heat-2{background:rgba(212,147,30,0.25);color:rgba(212,147,30,0.8)}
.heat-3{background:rgba(212,147,30,0.45);color:#d4931e}
.heat-4{background:rgba(212,147,30,0.65);color:#e8a832}
.heat-5{background:rgba(212,147,30,0.85);color:#f0c060}

/* ─ SCATTER (D3 SVG) ─ */
#scatter-svg{width:100%;overflow:visible}

/* ─ REGION CARDS ─ */
.region-card{padding:28px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--bg2);position:relative;overflow:hidden;cursor:default;transition:border-color 0.2s}
.region-card:hover{border-color:var(--border2)}
.region-card::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:var(--rc-color,var(--dim))}
.region-name{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:300;margin-bottom:4px}
.region-count{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:var(--dim);margin-bottom:20px;text-transform:uppercase}
.region-avg{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:48px;font-weight:300;line-height:1;color:var(--rc-color,var(--gold))}
.region-unit{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-left:4px}
.region-bars{margin-top:16px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}
.region-bar-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--dim)}
.region-bar-track{flex:1;height:3px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06);border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden}
.region-bar-fill{height:100%;border-radius:2px;transition:width 1.2s cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1);width:0}
.region-bar-val{width:28px;text-align:right}

/* ─ SPOTLIGHT ─ */
.spotlight-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1px;background:var(--border)}
.spotlight-cell{background:var(--bg2);padding:28px 24px;transition:background 0.2s;cursor:default}
.spotlight-cell:hover{background:var(--bg3)}
.sp-flag{font-size:32px;margin-bottom:12px}
.sp-country{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:4px}
.sp-tag{display:inline-block;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:3px 8px;border-radius:2px;margin-bottom:14px}
.sp-story{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.65}
.sp-nums{display:flex;gap:16px;margin-top:14px;padding-top:14px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.sp-num-item{flex:1}
.sp-num-label{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:8px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--dim);margin-bottom:3px}
.sp-num-val{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:300}

/* ─ WORLD MAP ─ */
#map-wrap{width:100%;position:relative}
#map-svg{width:100%;display:block}
.map-ctrls{display:flex;gap:8px;margin-bottom:24px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.map-btn{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:7px 16px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:transparent;color:var(--muted);cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.15s}
.map-btn:hover{border-color:var(--border2);color:var(--text)}
.map-btn.on{border-color:var(--accent);background:rgba(212,184,150,0.08);color:var(--accent)}
.map-legend{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-top:16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--dim)}
.map-legend-bar{display:flex;height:8px;border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden;width:200px}

/* ─ TOOLTIP ─ */
.tt{position:fixed;background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border2);padding:14px 18px;font-size:12px;pointer-events:none;z-index:9000;display:none;min-width:180px;box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.6)}
.tt-name{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:400;margin-bottom:10px;color:var(--text)}
.tt-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:24px;margin-top:4px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted)}
.tt-row span:last-child{color:var(--text)}

/* ─ TREEMAP ─ */
#treemap-svg{width:100%;display:block}

/* ─ TABLE ─ */
.tbl-controls{display:flex;gap:12px;margin-bottom:20px;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.tbl-search{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:12px;padding:9px 14px;outline:none;width:260px;transition:border 0.2s}
.tbl-search:focus{border-color:var(--border2)}
.tbl-filter{display:flex;gap:4px}
.tbl-f-btn{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:7px 12px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:transparent;color:var(--muted);cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.15s}
.tbl-f-btn:hover{color:var(--text)}
.tbl-f-btn.on{background:var(--surface);color:var(--text);border-color:var(--border2)}
.tbl-count{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--dim);margin-left:auto}
table.dt{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse}
table.dt thead th{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--dim);padding:10px 12px;text-align:left;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);cursor:pointer;user-select:none;white-space:nowrap;transition:color 0.15s}
table.dt thead th:hover{color:var(--muted)}
table.dt thead th.sort-a::after{content:' ↑';color:var(--accent)}
table.dt thead th.sort-d::after{content:' ↓';color:var(--accent)}
table.dt tbody tr{border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);transition:background 0.12s;cursor:default}
table.dt tbody tr:hover{background:var(--surface)}
table.dt tbody td{padding:10px 12px;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}
table.dt tbody td:first-child{color:var(--text);font-weight:500}
table.dt tbody td.num{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;text-align:right;font-size:11px}
.pill-dom{display:inline-block;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:2px}
.pill-beer{background:rgba(212,147,30,0.15);color:var(--beer)}
.pill-spirits{background:rgba(192,57,43,0.15);color:var(--spirits)}
.pill-wine{background:rgba(142,68,173,0.15);color:var(--wine)}
.pill-none{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);color:var(--dim)}
.mini-spark{display:inline-flex;gap:2px;align-items:flex-end;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:6px}
.mini-spark span{display:inline-block;width:5px;border-radius:1px}
.tbl-page{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;margin-top:16px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--dim)}
.tbl-pg-btns{display:flex;gap:4px}
.pg-b{padding:4px 10px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:transparent;color:var(--muted);font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.15s}
.pg-b:hover,.pg-b.on{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent)}

/* ─ LEGEND ─ */
.legend{display:flex;gap:24px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:16px}
.legend-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--muted)}
.legend-swatch{width:12px;height:12px;border-radius:2px}

/* ─ FOOTER ─ */
footer{padding:60px 80px 40px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.footer-top{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;gap:40px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:40px}
.footer-brand{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:40px;font-weight:300;color:var(--gold)}
.footer-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;max-width:380px;margin-top:8px}
.footer-links{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px}
.footer-links a{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:var(--dim);text-decoration:none;transition:color 0.15s}
.footer-links a:hover{color:var(--text)}
.footer-bottom{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.footer-copy{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--dim)}
.tech-stack{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.tech-tag{font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;border:1px solid var(--border);padding:3px 9px;color:var(--dim)}

/* ─ ANIMATE ON SCROLL ─ */
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px);transition:opacity 0.6s ease,transform 0.6s ease}
.reveal.visible{opacity:1;transform:none}
.reveal-delay-1{transition-delay:0.1s}
.reveal-delay-2{transition-delay:0.2s}
.reveal-delay-3{transition-delay:0.3s}
.reveal-delay-4{transition-delay:0.4s}

@media(max-width:900px){
  .section,.hero{padding:80px 24px}
  nav{padding:0 24px}
  .nav-links{display:none}
  .two-col,.three-col,.spotlight-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .hero-counter{display:none}
  footer{padding:40px 24px}
  .footer-top{flex-direction:column}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="progress"></div>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-brand">PROOF</div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#findings">Findings</a>
    <a href="#regions">By Region</a>
    <a href="#portraits">Portraits</a>
    <a href="#map">World Map</a>
    <a href="#data">Full Data</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ═══ HERO ═══ -->
<div class="hero" id="top">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-counter" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="hero-num" id="hero-count">193</div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-eyebrow">A Data Study · WHO Global Report</div>
  <h1 class="hero-title">What the<br>World <em>Drinks</em></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">An analysis of alcohol consumption across 193 nations — who drinks what, how much, and why the patterns reveal deep cultural, geographic, and economic divides.</p>
  <div class="hero-meta">
    <div class="hero-meta-item">
      <div class="hero-meta-label">Countries studied</div>
      <div class="hero-meta-val">193<span class="hero-meta-unit">nations</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-meta-item">
      <div class="hero-meta-label">Heaviest drinker</div>
      <div class="hero-meta-val">Belarus<span class="hero-meta-unit">14.4L / yr</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-meta-item">
      <div class="hero-meta-label">Beer champion</div>
      <div class="hero-meta-val">Namibia<span class="hero-meta-unit">376 servings</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-meta-item">
      <div class="hero-meta-label">Spirit champion</div>
      <div class="hero-meta-val">Grenada<span class="hero-meta-unit">438 servings</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-hint">SCROLL</div>
</div>

<!-- ═══ SECTION 1: KEY FINDINGS ═══ -->
<section class="section" id="findings">
  <div class="section-label" data-n="01">Key Findings</div>
  <h2 class="section-title reveal">The numbers that<br><em>surprised</em> us</h2>
  <p class="section-body reveal">The dataset — drawn from the WHO Global Status Report — measures per-person annual consumption across beer, spirits, and wine for 193 countries. What emerges isn't just a list of statistics. It's a map of culture, religion, history, and climate painted in servings per year.</p>

  <div class="three-col" style="margin-bottom:48px">
    <div class="stat-block reveal reveal-delay-1" style="--sb-color:var(--beer)">
      <div class="stat-num">52%</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Nations where beer dominates</div>
      <div class="stat-note">101 of 180 drinking countries choose beer as their primary beverage — the universal language of alcohol.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-block reveal reveal-delay-2" style="--sb-color:var(--spirits)">
      <div class="stat-num">13</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Countries reporting zero</div>
      <div class="stat-note">Afghanistan, Iran, Pakistan, and 10 others report zero consumption — mostly majority-Muslim nations where alcohol is culturally or legally prohibited.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-block reveal reveal-delay-3" style="--sb-color:var(--wine)">
      <div class="stat-num">3.7×</div>
      <div class="stat-label">Europe vs. Asia gap</div>
      <div class="stat-note">Europe averages 8.7L pure alcohol per person per year. Asia averages just 2.0L — a 3.7× difference driven by culture, religion, and income.</div>
